 Courses</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressTavern/~3/n96enm9M4zU/wp-abtesting-split-testing-as-a-service'' title=''There is a new up and coming AB Split testing service for WordPress called WP-ABTesting that aims to help you optimize websites based on data, not opinions. Anytime I’ve heard of anyone wanting an A/B testing plugin, I’ve referred them to ShrimpTest by Mitcho and Automattic however, it appears that development on that plugin has ceased as it hasn’t been upda [&hellip;]''>WPTavern: WP-ABTesting – Split Testing As A Service</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
