(19, 2, '2013-05-22 11:14:01', '2013-05-22 11:14:01', '<strong>Patent Search Links</strong><br>\r\n				\r\n				<a href=''http://www.uspto.gov/patft/index.html''  target="_blank">United States Patent Searches</a><br>\r\n				<a href=''http://www.uspto.gov/main/trademarks.htm''  target="_blank">United States TradeMark Searches</a><br>\r\n				<a  href=''http://www.ibiblio.org/patents/index.html''  target="_blank"	>Index to Manual of Classification of Patents</a><br>\r\n				<a href=''http://www.ibiblio.org/patents/intropat.html''  target="_blank">STO''s Internet Patent Search System</a><br>\r\n				<a href=''http://portal.uspto.gov/external/portal/pair''  target="_blank">US Patent Application Information Retrieval (PAIR)</a><br>\r\n				<a href=''http://ofi.epoline.org/view/GetDossier?dosnum=%E2%8C%A9=EN''  target="_blank"	>EPO Search Status</a><br>\r\n				<br>\r\n				<br>\r\n				<strong>Patent Offices</strong><br>\r\n				<br>\r\n				<a href=''http://www.wipo.int''  target="_blank">World Intellectual Property Organization (WIPO)</a><br>\r\n				<a href=''http://www.uspto.gov''  target="_blank">U S Patent Office</a><br>\r\n				<a href=''http://www.european-patent-office.org/index.htm''  target="_blank">European Patent Office</a><br>\r\n				<a href=''http://www.justice.gov.il/MOJEng/Registrar+of+Pledge/RashamPatentim''  target="_blank">Israel Ministry of Justice – Patent Office</a><br>\r\n				<br>\r\n				\r\n\r\n				<br>\r\n				<strong>Intellectual Property - General Information</strong><br>\r\n				<br>\r\n				<a href=''http://www.law.emory.edu/fedcircuit/fedcasearch.html''  target="_blank">U S Federal Circuit Case Search</a><br>\r\n				<a href=''http://www.uspto.gov/web/offices/pac/doc/general/''  target="_blank">General Patent Information</a><br>\r\n				<a href=''http://www.law.emory.edu/fedcircuit/''  target="_blank">Decisions of the Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit</a><br>\r\n				<a href=''http://www4.law.cornell.edu/uscode/''  target="_blank">U S Code</a><br>\r\n