(537, 2, '2013-08-19 07:09:56', '2013-08-19 07:09:56', 'The firm helps clients identify, determine, and broaden the protection scope of their core Intellectual Property. This is achieved by analyzing and assessing the potential business opportunities that may emerge from the client’s innovative technologies and areas of invention. Ehrlich &amp; Fenster strategic advantage is in its ability to identify the individual or multi-core technologies often hidden within a technological development. The firm pursues all the potential business directions available to a client including buying, in-and-out licensing, selling and international expansion.\r\n\r\nEach department is involved in drafting and prosecuting patent applications, including opposition procedures, in rendering opinions regarding IP matters, IP related Due Diligence processes, and in devising IP and commercialization strategies. There are over a dozen patent attorneys having Ph.D. degrees in all disciplines, with most Department heads having a doctorate degree.\r\n\r\nEhrlich &amp; Fenster provides patent prosecution services in a broad range of technologies to many small and mid-sized companies, as well as to large clients that have critical timing requirements, complex patent applications likely to be embroiled in litigation or interferences, or require specialized technical needs.\r\n\r\nAmong our practice areas:\r\n\r\n Biotech, Immunology, Agrotechnology, Bioinformatics, Biochemistry\r\n\r\n Pharmacology, Chemistry\r\n\r\n Physics, Mechanics, Medical Devices, Cleantech\r\n\r\n Electronics, Elecrooptics, Computer Hardware\r\n\r\n Computer Software, Telecommunications, Business Methods\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Patents', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '535-revision-2', '', '', '2013-08-19 07:09:56', '2013-08-19 07:09:56', '', 535, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=537', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(538, 2, '2013-07-24 13:22:46', '2013-07-24 13:22:46', 'Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source. Lorem Ipsum comes from sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 of "de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum" (The Extremes of Good and Evil) by Cicero, written in 45 BC. This book is a treatise on the theory of ethics, very popular during the Renaissance. The first line of Lorem Ipsum, "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet..", comes from a line in section 1.10.32.\r\n\r\nThe standard chunk of Lorem Ipsum used since the 1500s is reproduced below for those interested. Sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 from "de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum" by Cicero are also reproduced in their exact original form, accompanied by English versions from the 1914 translation by H. Rackham.', 'Trademarks', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '35-revision-5', '', '', '2013-07-24 13:22:46', '2013-07-24 13:22:46', '', 35, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=538', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(539, 2, '2013-08-19 07:12:14', '2013-08-19 07:12:14', 'Nowadays, industrial design and the aesthetic features of products are becoming increasingly more important to both companies and consumer. A Design protects the overall visual appearance of a product or a part of a product, resulting from its features- contours, colors, shape, texture or materials. Meaning, legal protection is given to the way the product looks. A Registered Design can be a valuable intellectual property right, as it may create the basis of an infringement action.\r\n\r\nOur Design Department, specializes in identifying the needs of each and every client, especially those whose products are seasonal in nature and require expedited processing. Our design department also specializes in preparing and filing Design application in Israel and abroad, as well as in design patents prosecution and enforcement. In filing design applications, as in all other aspects, we ensure achievement of our clients business goals in the procurement of strong IP portfolio and combined strategy.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Design', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'design', '', '', '2013-08-20 14:13:55', '2013-08-20 14:13:55', '', 98, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?page_id=539', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(540, 2, '2013-08-19 07:11:40', '2013-08-19 07:11:40', '', 'Designs', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '539-revision', '', '', '2013-08-19 07:11:40', '2013-08-19 07:11:40', '', 539, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=540', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(541, 2, '2013-08-19 07:12:59', '2013-08-19 07:12:59', 'The Litigation Support department deals with cases which involve actual or potential litigation or which involve due diligence or analysis of patents or patent portfolios during acquisition or investment.\r\n\r\nWe advise clients on preparing for litigation and help clients to find suitable representation overseas. We continue to be involved in the technical and interface aspects of these litigations remaining deeply involved in these cases during their entire lifetime. We have had a major part in cases of this type in the US, the EPO, the UK, Germany, Japan, China and Singapore. We also represent clients in discussions with foreign patent holders who assert their patents against our clients.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Litigation Support', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'litigation-support', '', '', '2013-08-19 07:12:59', '2013-08-19 07:12:59', '', 98, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?page_id=541', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(542, 2, '2013-08-19 07:12:34', '2013-08-19 07:12:34', '', 'Litigation Support', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '541-revision', '', '', '2013-08-19 07:12:34', '2013-08-19 07:12:34', '', 541, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=542', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(543, 2, '2013-08-19 07:13:40', '2013-08-19 07:13:40', 'Plant breeders'' rights are rights granted to the breeder of a new variety of plant that give him exclusivity over the propagating material (including seed, cuttings, divisions, tissue culture) and harvested material (cut flowers, fruit, foliage) of a new variety for a number of years.\r\n\r\nSeed is submitted to the official plant variety office to check that it is distinct, stable, and uniform. If these tests are passed, exclusive rights are granted for a period of 20 years (or 25 years, for trees and vines). Annual renewal fees are required to maintain the rights.\r\n\r\nThe Breeders Rights Department handles the submission and processing of such applications in Israel.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Breeder''s Rights', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'breeders-rights', '', '', '2013-08-19 07:13:40', '2013-08-19 07:13:40', '', 98, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?page_id=543', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(544, 2, '2013-08-19 07:13:33', '2013-08-19 07:13:33', 'Plant breeders'' rights are rights granted to the breeder of a new variety of plant that give him exclusivity over the propagating material (including seed, cuttings, divisions, tissue culture) and harvested material (cut flowers, fruit, foliage) of a new variety for a number of years.\n\nSeed is submitted to the official plant variety office to check that it is distinct, stable, and uniform. If these tests are passed, exclusive rights are granted for a period of 20 years (or 25 years, for trees and vines). Annual renewal fees are required to maintain the rights.\n\nThe Breeders Rights Department handles the submission and processing of such applications in Israel.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Breeder''s Rights', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '543-revision', '', '', '2013-08-19 07:13:33', '2013-08-19 07:13:33', '', 543, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=544', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(545, 2, '2013-08-19 07:14:13', '2013-08-19 07:14:13', 'Trade secrets are a common and powerful form of intellectual property, sometimes the most valued asset of the company. Businesses must be particularly careful when dealing with trade secrets because, unlike the case with patents or trademarks, failure to maintain the confidentiality required for trade secret protection can result in a complete loss of rights. Examples of trade secrets include, inter alia, technical information, formulas, germlines, germplasms, reproductive materials, genetic materials, databases, methods, processes, know-how, tolerances, computer programs, source codes, laboratory and research data, designs, improvements, product plans, SOPs and the like.\r\n\r\nBusinesses must understand the costs and benefits of different strategies for protecting intellectual property. Some forms of protection, including patent protection and trade secret protection, overlap. Knowing when to protect valuable information as a trade secret and when to protect it through patent procurement is vital to managing and optimizing such assets. Our patent attorneys are experienced in the relative strengths and weaknesses of patent versus trade secret protection that can help determine whether to maintain an invention as a trade secret, seek a patent or maintain a portion thereof as a trade secret, while securing patent protection to the remainder portions.\r\n\r\nEhrlich &amp; Fenster works with its clients to establish appropriate procedures to secure their sensitive information. When we encounter an invention or development for which the best IP protection is a trade secret we counsel our clients how to effectively protect the trade secret and to nevertheless generate value for the company.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEhrlich &amp; Fenster offers a service that includes:\r\n\r\n1. Identifying the trade secret;\r\n\r\n2. Integrating the secret in the IP portfolio of the client;\r\n\r\n3. Documenting the trade secret;\r\n\r\n4. Trade secret depository;\r\n\r\n5. Creating a reminder system for monitoring updates of the trade secret;\r\n\r\n6. When needed, updating the trade secret on a periodic basis;\r\n\r\n7. Guiding the client how to protect the secret;\r\n\r\n8. Assisting in protecting the secret;\r\n\r\n9. Forming a legal situation whereby breach of confidentiality will more likely be enforceable against a third party; and\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Trade Secrets', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'trade-secrets', '', '', '2013-08-19 07:14:23', '2013-08-19 07:14:23', '', 98, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?page_id=545', 0, 'page', '', 0),
