(547, 2, '2013-08-19 07:16:36', '2013-08-19 07:16:36', 'Nowadays, industrial design and the aesthetic features of products are becoming increasingly more important to both companies and consumer. A Design protects the overall visual appearance of a product or a part of a product, resulting from its features- contours, colors, shape, texture or materials. Meaning, legal protection is given to the way the product looks. A Registered Design can be a valuable intellectual property right, as it may create the basis of an infringement action.\n\nOur Design Department, specializes in identifying the needs of each and every client, especially those whose products are seasonal in nature and require expedited processing. Our design department also specializes in preparing and filing Design application in Israel and abroad, as well as in design patents prosecution and enforcement. In filing design applications, as in all other aspects, we ensure achievement of our clients business goals in the procurement of strong IP portfolio and combined strategy.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Design', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '539-autosave', '', '', '2013-08-19 07:16:36', '2013-08-19 07:16:36', '', 539, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=547', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
